Description: Test Steps:
1. openBrowser("")
2. navigateToUrl(AdactinUrl)
3. applicationKeyword.WebKeywords.login(Username, Password, findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Hotel Reservation System/Spy_inputUsername"), findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Hotel Reservation System/Spy_inputPassword"), findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Hotel Reservation System/Spy_loginButton"))
4. selectOptionByValue(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_Select Location"), Location, true)
5. selectOptionByValue(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_Select Hotel"), HotelName, true)
6. selectOptionByValue(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_Select Room Type"), RoomType, true)
7. setText(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_inputdatepick_in"), CheckInDate)
8. setText(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_inputdatepick_out"), CheckOutDate)
9. click(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/SpySubmit"))
10. verifyMatch(Location, "Sydney", false)
11. applicationKeyword.WebKeywords.logout(findTestObject("Adactin/AdactinSpy/Page_Adactin.com - Search Hotel/Spy_Logout"))
12. closeBrowser()
